data.description:
PRICE TO SELL!
This home offers a perfect blend of country living with a touch of city style! The property boasts a picturesque view overlooking a tranquil creek. Inside, you'll find a spacious living room complete with a charming rock fireplace, a dedicated office space, a versatile room that can be used as a game or hobby room, and a formal dining area. With 1.71 acres of land, you can savor Amarillo's stunning sunsets. Additionally, there's a convenient storage building located at the rear of the property. Reach out today to schedule a private viewing of this exceptional property!
